==English==

===Verb===
'''[[chicken]] [[out]]'''
#{{idiom}}  To [[shy away]] from a daring task; to [[decline]], [[refuse]], or [[avoid]] something due to [[fear]] or [[uncertainty]].
#:''We almost convinced his mom to ride the roller coaster, but she '''chickened out''' when she saw how high it went.''

